## TMF API Reference: TMF633 - Service Catalog Management
Version 4.0 The Service Catalog API is one of Catalog
Management API Family. Service Catalog API goal is to
provide a catalog of services. Service Catalog API performs
the following operations on the resource : - Retrieve an
entity or a collection of entities depending on filter
criteria - Partial update of an entity (including updating
rules) - Create an entity (including default values and
creation rules) - Delete an entity (for administration
purposes) - Manage notification of events. . Copyright Â©
